name: Guadalajara
description: This is a very special song. It is the first music of the Cuban jazz genre commercialized as NFT. It was recorded at the Viejalinda Record studios by Adolfo Martinez (Fito) in Havana, Cuba. Piano: Ernesto Cisneros. Bass: Israel López. Drums: Maikel Pérez. Guitar: Dairon Rodríguez. The song was composed by Israel López and Ernesto Cisneros in Guadalajara, Mexico in 1999 and now it is finally recorded. By decision of the group, all profits generated by this music will be distributed equally among all participants.
